title: DDFP 420: Wild Card Review & Greatest Catches
itunes:title: DDFP 420: Wild Card Review & Greatest Catches
description:
Shek sits down with Maurice Jones-Drew, Ike Taylor, and Handsome Hank to break down all the action from Wild Card Weekend. Is Martavis Bryant's catch better than Odell Beckham Jrs? Who had the more painful loss? Did Shek really compare himself to Kyrie Irving? Find out more on DDFP.  Watch the full show here: https://youtu.be/bvs4x01M2qE
